{"tid":2037754,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"楊岳橋：建制派議員應該燒毁他們的外國護照","createTime":"2020-05-27T07:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T07:35:31.000Z","uid":2054,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"59bee77346c3d840b3ea17cb76816c4b52a2df55","tid":2037754,"uid":2054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:13:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2476350/楊岳橋:建制議員持外國護照亦屬國安漏洞\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2476350%2F%E6%A5%8A%E5%B2%B3%E6%A9%8B%3A%E5%BB%BA%E5%88%B6%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8C%81%E5%A4%96%E5%9C%8B%E8%AD%B7%E7%85%A7%E4%BA%A6%E5%B1%AC%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E&d=y71HX3BFsGTccDILyV%2F8U1DHT90Y5dJ0llo76wtTvPU%3D&h=459551cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2476350/楊岳橋:建制議員持外國護照亦屬國安漏洞</a><br />\n<br />\n今日 12:30   AAA<br />\n港區人大代表陳曼琪日前在港區人大小組會議發言，提出設立國家安全專屬法庭，並規定由無外國居留權的中國籍香港永久居民任法官。公民黨楊岳橋不點名批評指屬愚昧和忘本，忘記自己在香港接受法律教育。<br />\n<br />\n楊岳橋認為，如果外國法官被認為有問題，手持外國護照的建制派議員也將是國家安全的漏洞，應該燒毁他們的外國護照。"},{"pid":"25c3488cd57275740eba590c6a9ca063c6afd37b","tid":2037754,"uid":325346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:15:32.000Z","msg":"直選議員無外國護照<br />\n功能組別就有啦"},{"pid":"aefdfffa8a55d23515555d74bda58e93572725bb","tid":2037754,"uid":27416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:19:40.000Z","msg":"你個dead body 呢唔好忘本"},{"pid":"08852705dec28fe5c7057da7300014a468dc5bf3","tid":2037754,"uid":55458,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:21:38.000Z","msg":"你唔係法醫官<br />\n唔可以燒人哋護照"},{"pid":"d81aedf52d3849920e74cd6449dac58ada1a8aa0","tid":2037754,"uid":262389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T07:35:31.000Z","msg":"[文宣方向][跳出同溫層]民意調查分析<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2037458\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2037458</a>"}]}